### Embed Instruction Queue System (TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/packages/embeds/README.md

Demonstrates the instruction queue mechanism used when the embed iframe is not yet ready. Commands are stored in a queue and executed once the iframe is initialized.

```typescript
type Instruction = SingleInstruction | SingleInstruction[];
type InstructionQueue = Instruction[];

// Commands are queued if iframe isn't ready
if (!this.iframeReady) {
  this.iframeDoQueue.push(doInIframeArg);
  return;
}
```

