### Enable Embed Logging - URL Parameter

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/packages/embeds/README.md

Activates logging for the Cal.com embed by appending a specific query parameter to the page URL. This is crucial for diagnosing issues with the embed by providing detailed logs from both the parent page and the iframe. The parameter `cal.embed.logging=1` enables this feature.

```text
https.example.com/contact?cal.embed.logging=1
```

