### Embed Cal.com Calendar using Shortcode

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/packages/app-store/wordpress/DESCRIPTION.md

This shortcode allows you to embed your Cal.com booking calendar into any WordPress page or post. You can specify the calendar URL, embed type (inline or popup), and customize the button text for popup embeds.

```html
[cal url="/username/meetingid" type=2 text="Schedule a call with me"]
```

