### Cal.com Embed Parent-to-Iframe Commands

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/packages/embeds/LIFECYCLE.md

Defines the available commands that the parent window can send to the Cal.com iframe to control its UI, acknowledge readiness, or initiate embedding with specific configurations.

```json
