### Forward Query Parameters - JavaScript

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/packages/embeds/README.md

Enables automatic forwarding of query parameters from the parent page to the Cal.com iframe. This configuration must be set immediately after the embed snippet is added to the page. Ensure `Cal.config` is initialized if it doesn't exist.

```javascript
Cal.config = Cal.config || {};
Cal.config.forwardQueryParams=true
```

