### Add Floating Action Button - TypeScript

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/packages/embeds/README.md

Embeds a floating action button that opens the Cal.com calendar in a modal window. This functionality relies on Cal.com's modal embedding system. Configuration includes the calendar link, button text, and button position.

```typescript
Cal.floatingButton({
  calLink: "organization/event-type",
  buttonText: "Book meeting",
  buttonPosition: "bottom-right"
});
```

